quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,31,"(Ànábì ’Ibrọ̄hīm) sọ pé: “Kí tún ni ọ̀rọ̀ tí ẹ bá wá, ẹ̀yin Òjíṣẹ́?”",""
  51,32,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Dájúdájú Wọ́n rán wa níṣẹ́ sí ìjọ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ ni",""
  51,33,"nítorí kí á lè fi òkúta amọ̀ (sísun) ránṣẹ́ sí wọn.",""
  51,34,"Wọ́n ti fi àmì sí i lára lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ fún àwọn alákọyọ.”",""
  51,35,"Nítorí náà, A mú àwọn tó jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo jáde kúrò nínú (ìlú náà).",""
  51,36,"A kò sì rí nínú (ìlú náà) yàtọ̀ sí ilé kan tó jẹ́ ti àwọn mùsùlùmí.",""
  51,37,"A sì fi àmì kan sílẹ̀ nínú (ìlú náà) fún àwọn tó ń páyà ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro.",""
  51,38,"(Àmì tún wà) lára (Ànábì) Mūsā. Nígbà tí A fi ẹ̀rí pọ́nńbélé rán an níṣẹ́ sí Fir‘aon.",""
  51,39,"Ṣùgbọ́n ó lo gbogbo agbára rẹ̀ láti kẹ̀yìn sí òdodo. Ó sì wí pé: “Òpìdán tàbí wèrè kan (nìyí).”",""
  51,40,"Nítorí náà, A mú òun àti àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀. A sì jù wọ́n sínú agbami odò nígbà tí ó jẹ́ alábùkù.",""
  51,41,"(Àmì tún wà) lára ìjọ ‘Ād. (Rántí) nígbà tí A rán atẹ́gùn ìparun sí wọn.",""
  51,42,"Kò fi kiní kan tó fẹ́ sí lára sílẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀ àfi kí ó sọ ọ́ di n̄ǹkan tó kẹfun.<sup>1</sup>","[1] “n̄ǹkan tó kẹfun” ni n̄ǹkan tí ó ti gbó mọ́lẹ̀ tayọ dídámọ̀."
  51,43,"(Àmì tún wà) lára ìjọ Thamūd. (Rántí) nígbà tí A sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ jayé fún ìgbà díẹ̀ ná.”",""
  51,44,"Wọ́n ṣègbéraga sí àṣẹ Olúwa wọn. Nítorí náà, iná láti ojú sánmọ̀ gbá wọn mú; wọ́n sì ń wò bọ̀ọ̀.",""
  51,45,"Wọn kò lè dìde nàró. Wọn kò sì lè ran ara wọn lọ́wọ́.",""
  51,46,"Àti ìjọ Nūh tí ó ṣíwájú (wọn), dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ìjọ arúfin.",""
  51,47,"Àti pé sánmọ̀, A mọ ọ́n (sí òkè yín) pẹ̀lú agbára. Dájúdájú Àwa sì ni Alágbára (tí a mú un tóbi).",""
  51,48,"Àti ilẹ̀, A ṣe é ní ìtẹ́. (Àwa sì ni) olùtẹ́-ilẹ̀ sílẹ̀ tó dára.",""
  51,49,"Àti pé gbogbo n̄ǹkan ni A ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ ní oríṣi méjì-méjì nítorí kí ẹ lè lo ìrántí.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Yāsīn; 36:36."
  51,50,"Nítorí náà, ẹ sá lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu (nípa ìronúpìwàdà). Dájúdájú èmi ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé fún yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀.",""
  51,51,"Ẹ má ṣe mú ọlọ́hun mìíràn mọ́ Allāhu. Dájúdájú èmi ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé fún yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀.",""
